verbose_text: As shown in XREF_TABLE, alpha-ESA (C18 :3, n-5), gamma-linolenic acid (C18 :3, n-6), and alpha-linolenic acid (C18 :3, n-3), which belong to the triunsaturated fatty acid group, substantially inhibited ED cell growth (IC 50 values of 8.9, 61.3 and 129.9 muM, respectively) and Su9T01 cell growth (IC 50 values of 29.3, 174.3 and 167.4 muM, respectively).
